cteristic strong silicate feature shows a weak positive correlation. A\ncomparison with a high-quality mid-IR spectrum of Mercury shows some moderate\nsimilarity to the results of this study, but does not explain all features.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 10:32:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
