 properties of acceleration in an individual\nflare from X-ray imaging spectroscopy alone, and can be applied to past,\ncurrent and future observations including those from RHESSI and Solar Orbiter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 14:56:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
