oposed\nalgorithm can estimate effectively the distribution of the fracture fields\nafter providing sufficient prior constraint information and hydraulic head\nmeasurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 02:55:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Feb 2023 02:01:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-08"}
